  "texts": [
    "Further, these synthetic images are assessed by calculating the fractal dimension of the cortical brain ribbons.",
    "The feasibility of this approach is illustrated by employing a cascade of adversarial networks that replicate various stages of the AD.",
    "However, training phase of the proposed model requires a significant amount of GPU memory and is also time consuming.",
    "Few others used Auto-encoder as the DL model.",
    "Pinaya et al. (2021) assessed structural neuroimaging data from AD and MCI patients to assess normative models based on deep autoencoders."
  ]
